CURVY actress Nkechi Blessing Sunday has taken to her Instagram account to give a word of wisdom. The actress said that discovering oneself will make you stay out of life drama and expectations from others. “Still thankful to those who said no to me,” she wrote. “It’s because of them I am doing it all by myself. Self-realization is the key to a life free of drama. “Know your worth and add tax ma Nigga. Road to 30… A lot of people are waiting on that bad news about you, may they wait until they perish in Jesus name.” The sexy Igbo actress became famous for her movie titled, ‘Omoge Lekki.’ She had since then upped her game with other movies she has featured in and also produced. She has become one of the established actresses in the Yoruba sector.